\fs24 \cf0 Humor Markers in Playful Chats:
\f0\b0  In playful conversations, the author\'92s 
\f1\b paralinguistic markers
\f0\b0  (emojis, elongated letters, onomatopoeia) and jokes abound. He leans into a goofy, sarcastic voice. For instance, when joking around with his girlfriend in a sexual-toned banter, he deliberately misspells and exaggerates: 
\f2\i \'93i already offered you me dick and you didn\'92t want it! \'85 har har har\'94
