\f1\b code-switch
\f0\b0  is striking: he can be bantering with a friend in one thread and using sincere, compassionate language with his partner in the next minute, tailoring his style instantly to the conversation\'92s seriousness.\

\f1\b Use of Slang and References:
\f0\b0  In playful mode, he loves slangy expressions (
