\f1\b Emphasis and Formatting:
\f0\b0  Another difference is how he conveys emphasis. In fun times, he\'92ll use goofy emphasis like 
\f2\i \'93SOOOOOO MUCH\'94
\f0\i0  in all-caps or repeated letters, as his girlfriend did when excited (
\f2\i \'93I love you SOOOOOO MUCH\'94
\f0\i0 ). He mirrors this energy with things like 
