\f3\i0 \uc0\u55357 \u56852 
\f2\i \'94
\f0\i0  \'96 mixing exaggeration with a cute emoji to show it\'92s half-joking, half-sincere. In serious mode, if he needs emphasis, he tends to either underscore it with actual seriousness (e.g. 
\f2\i \'93I\'92m 
\f5\b saying
