In summary, the author\'92s 
\f2\i linguistic fingerprint
\f0\i0  dynamically flexes across interpersonal contexts. He maintains core traits (informality, love of intensifiers, conversational flow) but 
\f1\b modulates them
\f0\b0 : dialing up tenderness or curtness, filtering slang in or out, and altering punctuation and structure to suit the relationship and emotional tenor. This adaptability reveals an acute sense of audience \'96 he unconsciously \'93code-switches\'94 between being a devoted boyfriend, a chill friend, a concerned son, or a combative partner, each with its own stylistic nuances. The consistent thread is that these mechanical choices are deliberate signals: he 
\f1\b self-presents
\f0\b0  as gentle and loving when in caring roles, and as raw and assertive when in conflict. His stylometric signature, therefore, isn\'92t a static set of habits, but a palette of behaviors that he selects from to navigate his social world \'96 showcasing an intuitive understanding of how to use language to serve empathy, assert needs, or share joy as the situation demands. Each mode \'96 romantic, friendly, playful, serious, supportive, argumentative \'96 is rendered in distinctive linguistic colors, all contributing to a richer, context-dependent portrait of the author\'92s communication style.\

